Create a ROS Package
Open a terminal:
cd ~/catkin_ws/src
catkin_create_pkg beginner_tutorials rospy std_msgs geometry_msgs
cd beginner_tutorials

Create URDF and Launch Directories
mkdir -p urdf launch
cd urdf

Create a Launch File:
cd ~/catkin_ws/src/beginner_tutorials/launch
gedit spawn_and_move.launch


Build the Workspace
cd ~/catkin_ws
catkin_make
source devel/setup.bash

Run the Simulation
roslaunch beginner_tutorials spawn_and_move.launch
